==English==
===Possessive pronoun===
'''y'all's'''

#(''regional, US'') Possessive of '''[[y'all]]''' (standing in for '''[[your]]''').
#:''Here are y'all's tickets for the show tonight.''
#(''regional, US'') Possessive of '''y'all''' (standing in for '''[[yours]]''').

